{"tid":585110,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"集思廣益：匿名電話每日打黎點做好","createTime":"2018-03-08T11:11:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T07:02:43.000Z","uid":175368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5f0f1d6bff78d5f0fa5190e0d4579abd3b716cae","tid":585110,"uid":175368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:11:02.000Z","msg":"我係絲，由兩個星期前開始有個匿名電話每日都打幾次黎，試過聽左但係冇人講野。到左琴日我又聽左一次，對方無啦啦講左句：「做咩唔聽我電話！」跟著就cut 線。再過幾分鐘又再打黎但係我冇聽，佢就留voice message diu 我老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知十幾分鐘黎突然有個有來電顯示ge電話打比我響一下未聽得切就cut 左線。緊接住就再用匿名電話打黎，冇聽又留voice message 叫我咁叻報警拉佢。<br />\n到底我報唔報警好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5237f441451d337c00726aed618cff0cbea75e18","tid":585110,"uid":69083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:12:27.000Z","msg":"公開佢有來電顯示個號碼"},{"pid":"dddea6dab0aaca384ed7165b782b026e05d2d028","tid":585110,"uid":175368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5237f441451d337c00726aed618cff0cbea75e18","tid":585110,"uid":69083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:12:27.000Z","msg":"公開佢有來電顯示個號碼"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:18:59.000Z","msg":"52799058 <br />\n我琴晚打過過去但係唔通，今朝佢又匿名打黎我跟手就再打但係都唔通。會唔會佢用緊兩個電話？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"193c8423715cf3abc323a5f974893f2245a2ee78","tid":585110,"uid":67455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:21:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6496ee8a008ea817cfb1fc366396712ca33667c6","tid":585110,"uid":145779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:22:21.000Z","msg":"根本由你應佢果一刻開始已經輸左"},{"pid":"d09ee89fa20b0db6f8aec37ec225cc3844485875","tid":585110,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike"